  "detailed_description": " <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1872710/extras/8edcc1c7e919e8b3a7237934e5a7c976.poster.avif?t=1723667324\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1872710/extras/8edcc1c7e919e8b3a7237934e5a7c976.webm?t=1723667324\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1872710/extras/8edcc1c7e919e8b3a7237934e5a7c976.mp4?t=1723667324\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Path To Gaea is a turn based puzzle-adventure that follows a simple story between good and evil. Take on the role of Kitsune and with the help of your little Wisp solve all the puzzles and discover the secret of Gaea's Crystal.<br><br><strong>Key features</strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Experience great visuals with a captivating soundtrack.<br></li><li> Fight enemies, overcome dangerous obstacles and escape deadly traps.<br></li><li> Undo System! Go back several steps and correct any wrong movement.<br></li><li> Difficult puzzles with moving platforms, switches, obstacles and spikes.<br></li><li> Collect hidden crystals to unlock new skins.<br></li><li> 12 Steam Achievements to unlock!</li></ul><br><br> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1872710/extras/7683e42635d14f43634934adf357d21f.poster.avif?t=1723667324\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1872710/extras/7683e42635d14f43634934adf357d21f.webm?t=1723667324\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1872710/extras/7683e42635d14f43634934adf357d21f.mp4?t=1723667324\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>New Undo System! – Go back several steps to avoid dying or to correct any wrong move by pressing the letter 'q' or 'rmb' (Once to activate it and again to step back).<br><br><br>As you progress, more elements are introduced – such as new enemies or trap types – gradually increasing the difficulty as the puzzles become more complex.<br><br> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1872710/extras/d189464dd759463d99a59f7294f99469.poster.avif?t=1723667324\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1872710/extras/d189464dd759463d99a59f7294f99469.webm?t=1723667324\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1872710/extras/d189464dd759463d99a59f7294f99469.mp4?t=1723667324\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Can you solve all the puzzles and uncover the mystery of Gaea's Crystal?",
